1. Download reference PDB. The downloaded pdb should be in the main folder, named dna_0.pdb.
2. Import the downloaded pdb into vmd.
3. Save each frame as its own gro file in "references" folder.

If the MD trjs are not in gro and trr files, then convert the trj to those files. 
1. Open cms and load traj dtr file in vmd
2. Save gro file with “first frame” and “last frame” using the same # and stride remains as 1. 
3. Gro file name should be “1.gro”
4. Save trr file with “first frame” as 0 and “last frame” as “100
5. Trr file name should be “1.trr”

Run trj_scoring and align scripts.
